60 Minutes KCBS 23.3 3. Home Improvement KABC 21.6 4. Roseanne KABC 21.5 5. 
Seinfeld KNBC 21.4 6. "American Music Awards" KABC 20.2 7. Frasier KNBC 19.4 8. 
Coach KABC 19.1 9. The Simpsons KTTV 18.8 10. Beverly Hills, 90210 KTTV 17.8 
