<P>
 Chapman and Concordia are two teams going in opposite directions and the 
Panthers won for the sixth time in seven games by defeating Concordia, 77-66, 
Tuesday night at Chapman. 
</P>
<P>
 The Panthers (15-7) led most of the way to hand the Eagles (15-12) their 
