<HEADLINE>
<P>
ESCAPING INMATE KILLED IN GARBAGE TRUCK COMPACTOR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A prisoner who apparently escaped in a garbage truck was found crushed to 
death in a landfill.Prison officials discovered that Anastasio Figueroa, 41, of 
Miami was missing Monday about 45 minutes after a garbage truck left the Hendry 
Correctional Institution. Guards later found his body at a landfill. He 
apparently had been crushed in the truck's compactor. 
</P>
