<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA021694-0094 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 013928 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 16, 1994, Wednesday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
