<HEADLINE>
<P>
SERVICE TODAY FOR HIEGERT'S FATHER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A rosary for Norbert John Hiegert, father of Cal State Northridge Athletic 
Director Bob Hiegert, will be said today at 6 p.m. at Gates, Kingsley & Gates 
Mortuary in Canoga Park. 
</P>
<P>
 Hiegert, 76, a resident of Woodland Hills, died Sunday of heart failure, a Cal 
State Northridge spokesman said. 
</P>
<P>
 Hiegert will be buried Thursday in Culver City after a 10 a.m. funeral Mass at 
St. Bernadine's Church, 24410 Calvert Ave., in Woodland Hills. 
</P>
