<P>
SHAKY BRIDGES, SHAKEN THEORIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Northridge earthquake showed that our freeway bridges are vulnerable. A 
Times Special Report examines efforts to make bridges safe and the policy 
choices facing government. 
</P>
